1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:09,000
You're an interesting human, Light Yagami.

2
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:16,500
Who are you?
How do you know my name?

3
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:24,000
I am the shinigami Ryuk.
I am the original owner of that Death Note.

4
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:31,500
A shinigami... I never imagined they actually existed.

5
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:39,000
I want to propose a deal to you.
The deal for the shinigami eyes.

6
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:46,500
If you possess the shinigami eyes, just by looking at
a human's face, you can see their name and remaining lifespan.

7
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:54,000
If you can see their name, you can write it in the notebook immediately.
Convenient, wouldn't you say?

8
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:01,500
But there is a price.
In exchange for obtaining the shinigami eyes, you lose half your remaining lifespan.

9
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:09,000
Half my lifespan?
I cannot agree to such a deal.

10
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:16,500
I must reign as the god of the new world for a long time.
I cannot afford to shorten my lifespan.

11
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:24,000
I see. Well, let me know whenever you change your mind.

12
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:31,500
I want to ask you one thing. Is it true that a human
who uses the Death Note can go to neither heaven nor hell after death?

13
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:39,000
Yes, that is true.
A human who has touched the Death Note returns to nothingness.

14
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:46,500
I see... Even so, I do not mind.
My resolve will not change.

15
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:54,000
Even if I cannot go to heaven,
purifying this rotten world is my mission.

16
00:01:57,000 --> 00:02:01,500
Ryuk, all you need to do is watch.
Watch how I build the new world.

17
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:09,000
Interesting. Humans really are fascinating.
